==English==

===Etymology===
[F. gerbille. Cf. Jerboa.] 
===Noun===
'''gerbil''' ([[gerbils]])
#(Zoöl.) One of several species of small, jumping, murine rodents, of the genus Gerbillus. In their leaping powers they resemble the jerboa. They inhabit Africa, India, and Southern Europe.
